{"tid":635424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"或要與游蕙禎、劉小麗爭尾席　黃毓民轟梁天琦為游助選　無政治倫理是政棍","createTime":"2018-04-20T06:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T05:57:53.000Z","uid":51129,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5594c70c275b0e0edb81a9d9b672c1af5ec5e4da","tid":635424,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:21:04.000Z","msg":"立場報道2016/8/27 &mdash; 15:28<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民今天在facebook發佈街站直播片段，批評被禁參選的本土民主前線梁天琦，沒有協助出戰港島的熱血公民成員鄭錦滿，卻為游蕙禎助選，「不知這是什麼政治倫理 ... 未學行先學走，未做議員先做政棍」，他十分失望。<br />\n<br />\n據香港大學民研中心今天最新的滾動民調，九龍西最後的第六席，是劉小麗、青政的游蕙禎和爭取連任的黃毓民三名非建制派之爭，由於劉小麗支持度穩步上升入榜，資深議員黃毓民目前的支持度只有6%，落後游與劉3個百分點，僅排第七，勝算出現暗湧。黃的支持者近日已連番重點批評劉小麗的政綱和她過去在facebook的一些失言。<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民在直播片段中，除了批評民主黨的黃碧雲外，又指有人趁他近日生病較少出現街站，散播謠言。黃毓民指，除了民主派，他最失望的是一些剛剛參選、新加入的年輕人，都要抹黑和散佈謠言。他呼籲選民不要配票。<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民然後批評梁天琦，指港島區沒有青年新政的候選人，但梁都不幫助「熱普城」港島候選人鄭錦滿拉票，反而到九龍西他有份參選的地區，為游蕙禎助選，「不知這是什麼政治倫理 ... 未學行先學走，未做議員先做政棍 ... 好失望。」"},{"pid":"cf5cc1f737dd97b4f8215bc3308c51e5651152cb","tid":635424,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bba107115a0c1a744e06470143c074ddfeaebe","tid":635424,"uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:33:06.000Z","msg":"黃毓民收50萬 反 港 獨！"},{"pid":"6a066a5c28e41b3cbb22f27c268979a89fc9ee22","tid":635424,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:40:32.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"5820d372f7436256207330ba1e289cea62282fad","tid":635424,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3d7a337be2eca98e273e7879c54d363e6e3528","tid":635424,"uid":7369,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:59:09.000Z","msg":"毓民叫獨派支持永續基本法, 唔支持就係反骨仔政棍!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n......................選舉過咗幾個月, 毓民都話自己根本唔支持永續基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067cb9cb0dbab0a17135036d9237d90b56d12197","tid":635424,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f605027bf90f4c053168bfe76ad70f595f538df","tid":635424,"uid":39800,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"毓民點on9都好過柒頭本民ching<br />\n細細個睇tbb毓民學到好多野<br />\n🤣"},{"pid":"d34844f01928361c05f7c0765f4f15f79cad9e84","tid":635424,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"又反面，由草泥馬，陶君含，鳩達，國師，直到梁天恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n教主可以反幾次檯"},{"pid":"4de15ab3db0ae58a029e63705292b9acbe660199","tid":635424,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7f605027bf90f4c053168bfe76ad70f595f538df","tid":635424,"uid":39800,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"毓民點on9都好過柒頭本民ching<br />\n細細個睇tbb毓民學到好多野<br />\n🤣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"aggr, 我細細個就聽毓民講支持平反六四, 撐施君龍, 做個大中華膠!"},{"pid":"8cb2e38ff55abbb9f9cb510207d8726fcf5f8430","tid":635424,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19873e806e2549becc72a0e8b8cb59c605dd11ca","tid":635424,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cb2e38ff55abbb9f9cb510207d8726fcf5f8430","tid":635424,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike"